{"type":"message","id":"95bcf0a7","parentId":"83bd624c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:55:09.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:27","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\": \"oil prices Strait of Hormuz March 2026\", \"results\": [{\"title\": \"Oil prices to remain high for days with Strait of Hormuz in ... - Reuters\", \"url\": \"https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-expected-stay-high-days-all-eyes-strait-hormuz-flows-2026-03-02/\", \"snippet\": \"Bernstein raised its 2026 Brent oil price assumption from $65 to $80 a barrel, but sees prices reaching $120-$150 in an extreme case of\"}, {\"title\": \"Oil, gas prices spike as Iran war thrusts Strait of Hormuz into crisis\", \"url\": \"https://www.axios.com/2026/03/09/oil-prices-iran-war-strait-hormuz\", \"snippet\": \"Mar 9, 2026 - Business. Oil, gas prices spike as Iran war thrusts Strait of Hormuz into crisis ... The Iran war has cast a sharp spotlight on the global economy's reliance on the Strait of Hormuz. Why it matters: The strait\"}, {\"title\": \"Crude Oil Price Forecast | Strait of Hormuz Closure - Capital.com\", \"url\": \"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/crude-oil-price-forecast-09-03-2026\", \"snippet\": \"As of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, **US Crude Oil** ([US Crude](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1)) is trading at $76.29 per barrel, within an intraday range of $73.33�C$76.95. [**US Crude��s price**](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) trades at $76.29 as of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, holding well above its key moving-average cluster, with the 20/50/100/200-day SMAs stacked at roughly $67 / $63 / $61 / $63. [**Brent Crude��s price**](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) trades at $82.31 as of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, positioned above a tightly aligned moving-average cluster with the 20/50/100/200-day SMAs at approximately $72 / $67 / $65 / $66. ### Brent Crude Oil. The [Brent Crude price](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) tracked a similar arc, touching a two-year intraday high of $87.24 on 5 April 2024 amid a spike in regional risk premium, then retreating as supply-side pressures mounted. Yes, you can trade [**US Crude CFDs**](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) and [**Brent Crude CFDs**](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) on Capital.com.\"}, {\"title\": \"Oil prices spike above $70 per barrel as Iran's Straight of Hormuz ...\", \"url\": \"https://fortune.com/2026/03/02/oil-prices-spike-above-70-per-barrel-as-irans-straight-of-hormuz-grows-tangled/\", \"snippet\": Traceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\openclaw-tavily-search\\scripts\\tavily_search.py\", line 159, in <module>\r\n    main()\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\openclaw-tavily-search\\scripts\\tavily_search.py\", line 154, in main\r\n    json.dump(res, sys.stdout, ensure_ascii=False)\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python311\\Lib\\json\\__init__.py\", line 180, in dump\r\n    fp.write(chunk)\r\nUnicodeEncodeError: 'gbk' codec can't encode character '\\xa0' in position 217: illegal multibyte sequence\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":2088,"aggregated":"{\"query\": \"oil prices Strait of Hormuz March 2026\", \"results\": [{\"title\": \"Oil prices to remain high for days with Strait of Hormuz in ... - Reuters\", \"url\": \"https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-expected-stay-high-days-all-eyes-strait-hormuz-flows-2026-03-02/\", \"snippet\": \"Bernstein raised its 2026 Brent oil price assumption from $65 to $80 a barrel, but sees prices reaching $120-$150 in an extreme case of\"}, {\"title\": \"Oil, gas prices spike as Iran war thrusts Strait of Hormuz into crisis\", \"url\": \"https://www.axios.com/2026/03/09/oil-prices-iran-war-strait-hormuz\", \"snippet\": \"Mar 9, 2026 - Business. Oil, gas prices spike as Iran war thrusts Strait of Hormuz into crisis ... The Iran war has cast a sharp spotlight on the global economy's reliance on the Strait of Hormuz. Why it matters: The strait\"}, {\"title\": \"Crude Oil Price Forecast | Strait of Hormuz Closure - Capital.com\", \"url\": \"https://capital.com/en-int/market-updates/crude-oil-price-forecast-09-03-2026\", \"snippet\": \"As of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, **US Crude Oil** ([US Crude](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1)) is trading at $76.29 per barrel, within an intraday range of $73.33�C$76.95. [**US Crude��s price**](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) trades at $76.29 as of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, holding well above its key moving-average cluster, with the 20/50/100/200-day SMAs stacked at roughly $67 / $63 / $61 / $63. [**Brent Crude��s price**](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) trades at $82.31 as of 1.34pm UTC on 5 March 2026, positioned above a tightly aligned moving-average cluster with the 20/50/100/200-day SMAs at approximately $72 / $67 / $65 / $66. ### Brent Crude Oil. The [Brent Crude price](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) tracked a similar arc, touching a two-year intraday high of $87.24 on 5 April 2024 amid a spike in regional risk premium, then retreating as supply-side pressures mounted. Yes, you can trade [**US Crude CFDs**](/en-int/markets/commodities/us-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) and [**Brent Crude CFDs**](/en-int/markets/commodities/brent-crude-oil-spot-commodity-1) on Capital.com.\"}, {\"title\": \"Oil prices spike above $70 per barrel as Iran's Straight of Hormuz ...\", \"url\": \"https://fortune.com/2026/03/02/oil-prices-spike-above-70-per-barrel-as-irans-straight-of-hormuz-grows-tangled/\", \"snippet\": Traceback (most recent call last):\r\n  File \"C:\\Users\\Admini