{"type":"message","id":"39597215","parentId":"95bcf0a7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:55:09.959Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:28","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\": \"NATO Trump Europe defense March 2026\", \"results\": [{\"title\": \"In a World Order Defined by Trump, the Key to Europe's Defense Is ...\", \"url\": \"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/03/magazine/germany-europe-iran-merz-trump-defense.html\", \"snippet\": \"A few weeks after Trump vowed to take Greenland ��the easy way or the hard way,�� Chancellor Friedrich Merz of Germany acknowledged that Europeans committed to international law might soon find themselves overtaken by the new reigning logic of hard power. Yet Merz��s response over the weekend made good on his vow to press Europe��s geopolitical goals by speaking ��the language of power politics.�� He argued that this was ��not the moment to lecture our partners and allies,�� observing that European condemnations of Iranian violations of international law had ��achieved little over many years and decades,�� in part because Europe was ��not prepared to enforce fundamental interests, if necessary, with military force.�� In his meeting with Trump today, Merz represents a Europe that remains at odds with itself, even as its need to act in unison becomes more urgent by the hour.\"}, {\"title\": \"Trump Warns NATO's Future at Risk as Allies Refuse ... - YouTube\", \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AowNueInKDM\", \"snippet\": \"U.S. President Donald Trump said Sunday (March 15, 2026) that NATO faces a \\\"very bad\\\" future if U.S. allies fail to help open the Strait of\"}, {\"title\": \"Trump demands other countries help protect Strait of Hormuz as oil ...\", \"url\": \"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=27M2nhjg_OQ\", \"snippet\": \"... March 16, 2026. Hellen Rose. New. 5K views �� 9:55 �� Go to channel CNN ... Estonia Defense Minister reacts to Trump pressuring NATO on Strait of\"}, {\"title\": \"NAT